===============================================================================
                    Phase 4: 查询计划生成
===============================================================================

---------- Phase 4a: 单节点逻辑计划 ----------

  SE                  Planner              SNP
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | new Planner()      |
    |                  |-------------------->|
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | planner.plan(      |
    |                  |   parsedStmt,      |
    |                  |   analyzer,        |
    |                  |   tQueryOptions)   |
    |                  |-------------------->|
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | createSingleNode   |
    |                  | Plan(queryStmt,ctx)|
    |                  |------------------->|
    |                  |                    | createScanNode()
    |                  |                    |   -> OlapScanNode
    |                  |                    | createJoinNode()
    |                  |                    |   -> HashJoinNode
    |                  |                    | createAggregationPlan()
    |                  |                    |   -> AggregationNode
    |                  |                    | createSortPlan()
    |                  |                    |   -> SortNode
    |                  |                    | createSelectNode()
    |                  |                    |   -> SelectNode
    |                  | PlanNode Tree      |
    |                  | (单节点逻辑计划)     |
    |                  |<-------------------|

---------- Phase 4b: 物化视图选择 ----------

  SE                  Planner              MV
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | MaterializedView   |
    |                  | Selector.rewrite() |
    |                  |------------------->|
    |                  |                    | 尝试将查询重写为
    |                  |                    | 使用物化视图
    |                  | 重写后的 PlanNode   |
    |                  | Tree               |
    |                  |<-------------------|

---------- Phase 4c: 分布式计划生成 ----------

  SE                  Planner              DP
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | createPlanFragments|
    |                  | (root, ...)        |
    |                  |------------------->|
    |                  |                    | 递归遍历 PlanNode 树
    |                  |                    | 在数据交换边界切割
    |                  |                    | 插入 ExchangeNode
    |                  |                    | 选择分布策略:
    |                  |                    |   Colocate Join
    |                  |                    |   Bucket Shuffle Join
    |                  |                    |   Broadcast Join
    |                  |                    |   Shuffle Join
    |                  |                    | 多阶段聚合:
    |                  |                    |   本地预聚合
    |                  |                    |   Exchange + 合并聚合
    |                  | List<PlanFragment> |
    |                  | + ExchangeNode      |
    |                  |<-------------------|

---------- Phase 4d: 运行时过滤 & 最终化 ----------

  SE                  Planner              RF
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | generateRuntime    |
    |                  | Filters()          |
    |                  |------------------->|
    |                  |                    | 从 Join 谓词生成
    |                  |                    | IN (Bloom Filter)
    |                  |                    | MIN/MAX 过滤
    |                  |                    | 分配到 Probe 侧
    |                  |                    | ScanNode
    |                  |<-------------------|
    |                  |                    |
    |                  | PlanFragment.      |
    |                  | finalize()         |
    |                  |-------------------->|
    |                  |                    | DataSink 分配:
    |                  |                    |   DataStreamSink
    |                  |                    |   (中间 Fragment)
    |                  |                    |   ResultSink
    |                  |                    |   (根 Fragment)
    |                  |<-------------------|

