===============================================================================
                    Phase 6: BE 端执行 (Volcano Pull 模型)
===============================================================================

  PFE                 EN                   Scan                BR
    |                  |                    |                    |
    | open()           |                    |                    |
    |----------------->|                    |                    |
    |                  | _plan->open(state)  |                    |
    |                  |-------------------->|                    |
    |                  |                    |                    |
    |                  |                    | ExchangeNode.open() |
    |                  |                    |  创建 DataStreamRecvr|
    |                  |                    |                    |
    |                  |                    | OlapScanNode.open() |
    |                  |                    |  启动 Scanner 线程   |
    |                  |                    |-------------------->|
    |                  |                    |                    |
    |                  |                    |                    | BlockReader.init()
    |                  |                    |                    | 打开 RowsetReader
    |                  |                    |                    |
    |                  |                    |                    | 读取策略:
    |                  |                    |                    |  _direct_next_block()
    |                  |                    |                    |    (DUPLICATE KEY)
    |                  |                    |                    |  _direct_agg_key...
    |                  |                    |                    |    (AGGREGATE KEY)
    |                  |                    |                    |  _agg_key_next_block()
    |                  |                    |                    |    (多 rowset 合并)
    |                  |                    |                    |  _unique_key_next_block()
    |                  |                    |                    |    (UNIQUE KEY 版本合并)
    |                  |                    |                    |
    |                  |                    |                    | VCollectIterator
    |                  |                    |                    |  合并 Rowset/Segment
    |                  |                    |                    |
    |                  |                    | Block              |
    |                  |                    |<-------------------|
    |                  | Block              |                    |
    |                  |<-------------------|                    |
    |                  |                    |                    |

---------- 中间 Fragment: 数据发送 ----------

  PFE                 EN                   DS                   DR
    |                  |                    |                     |
    | [循环]            |                    |                     |
    |                  |                    |                     |
    | get_next(state,  |                    |                     |
    | block)           |                    |                     |
    |----------------->|                    |                     |
    |                  | Block              |                     |
    |<-----------------|                    |                     |
    |                  |                    |                     |
    | _sink->send(     |                    |                     |
    |   state, block)  |                    |                     |
    |------------------------------------------>                 |
    |                  |                    |                     |
    |                  |                    | Channel.send_block()|
    |                  |                    |                     |
    |                  |                    |---[远程]------------>|
    |                  |                    | brpc transmit_block()| VDataStreamMgr::
    |                  |                    |                     | transmit_block()
    |                  |                    |                     | -> add_block()
    |                  |                    |                     |
    |                  |                    |---[本地]------------>|
    |                  |                    | 直接 add 到          | VDataStreamRecvr::
    |                  |                    |  DataStreamRecvr     | add_block()
    |                  |                    |                     |
    | [循环直到 eos]    |                    |                     |
    |                  |                    |                     |

  流控: DataStreamRecvr 有 _total_buffer_limit
         缓冲超限时停止 ACK，提供反压

